List Sessions in a Volume.

Source: R/list_sessions_in_volume.R
list_sessions_in_volume.Rd

list_sessions_in_volume() has been superseded in list_sessions().

Usage

list_sessions_in_volume(vol_id = 1, vb = FALSE)

Arguments

vol_id

Target volume ID. Defaults to 1.

vb

Provide verbose output. Default is FALSE.

Value

A data frame with information about the sessions in a volume.

Examples

# \donttest{
list_sessions_in_volume() # Lists sessions in volume 1.
